        <footnote id="F7">On June 6, 2025, the Issuer's Compensation Committee approved a grant of RSUs, which are scheduled to vest as to 33% on each annual anniversary of the grant date until fully vested on June 6, 2028, subject to the Reporting Person's continued employment with the Issuer on each vesting date.</footnote>
